    <item>
      <title>金正恩称随着与俄罗斯关系加深，经济呈现“好转”态势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/kim-jong-un-says-economy-is-on-upturn-as-russian-ties-deepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩表示，朝鲜经济正在“明显好转”，朝鲜宣布成功试射了一枚新型战术弹道导弹，朝鲜可以将此枚导弹运往俄罗斯，以换取俄罗斯帮助朝鲜政权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/kim-jong-un-says-economy-is-on-upturn-as-russian-ties-deepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 02:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在赢得豁免权后寻求推翻纽约重罪判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-seeks-to-toss-ny-felony-conviction-after-immunity-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院裁定唐纳德·特朗普因其担任总统期间的行为而享有实质上的刑事起诉豁免权后，特朗普正努力争取撤销其在纽约的封口费定罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-seeks-to-toss-ny-felony-conviction-after-immunity-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 00:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
